de.must.markup
Class DataTableAdministration

java.lang.Object
  de.must.markup.Dialog
      de.must.markup.DataTableAdministration
All Implemented Interfaces:
Invokable
Direct Known Subclasses:
TypeAdministration
public abstract class DataTableAdministration
extends Dialog

Frame-like container to enclose input-output fields like text fields with database field association grid-like. Controls load and save actions. Used for property administration of a multiple database records. It is meant to contain several strorables like e.g. DataTextField.
